1. Kada se *bliži* kraj školske godine, deca postaju uzbuđena. (When the end of the school year *approaches*, children become excited.)
2. Udaljeni prijatelji postaju *bliži* kada ostanu u kontaktu. (Distant friends become *closer* when they stay in touch.)
3. Uvek mi je lakše kada je neko *bliži* meni u vreme stresnih situacija. (It's always easier for me when someone is *closer* to me during stressful situations.)
4. Kada se *približavaš* cilju, ne smeš da odustaneš. (When you *approach* your goal, you must not give up.)
5. Oni su *približili* stolice kako bi se lakše mogli razgovarati. (They *moved closer* the chairs so they could talk more easily.)
6. *Približno* znam koliko vremena mi je potrebno da stignem do posla. (I *approximately* know how much time it takes me to get to work.)
7. *Najbliži* restoran je udaljen pet minuta hoda odavde. (The *nearest* restaurant is a five-minute walk from here.)
8. Možemo li *približno* odrediti kada će doći paket? (Can we *roughly* estimate when the package will arrive?)